QuestData.Title: Traffic Issues
QuestData.Description: Yaungols are attacking our Burlap Trail. This is most bad fortune for grummles.$b$bWe use that trail to carry supplies to the Serpent's Spine. Without supplies, the defenders of the wall are in danger.$b$bGrummles are packers and explorers, not fighters. Could you be a luckydo for us and stop the yaungol blockade?
QuestData.CompletionText: A luckydon't travels a trail during a yaungol raid. A luckydo hires a big fighter type to help.
QuestData.RewardText: It is good fortune that a $r comes to help grummles. Good fortune to friend of grummles.
